Docker Installation
Docker installation commands
Ubuntu server
---->sudo apt-get update
----->sudo apt-get install docker docker.io
CentOS/RHEL
---->sudo yum -y install docker
----->sudo systemctl start docker
------->sudo systemctl enable docker
Verify the docker version
docker -v
